These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, milk, hot-chocolate, cola, lemonade, mirinda, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, nigerian, turkish, pakistani, russian, argentine, american
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, volleyball, ice-hockey, rugby, handball, cycling
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, car, helicopter, roller, tram, snowmobile, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is the pakistani##1
 3. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the nigerian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the thai is on the right of the american##1
 6. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the russian##1
 8. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the scooter and the argentine##2
 9. the russian is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the turkish##1
14. the argentine is the person driving the helicopter##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the american##1
16. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
17. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the turkish##1
18. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the russian##1
19. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | milk  | mirinda        | lemonade | hot-chocolate      | cola     | water      | almond-milk     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani         | american   | thai | argentine    | russian | turkish |
| Sport         | volleyball | rugby | lacrosse | snowboarding | cycling  | handball  | ice-hockey    |
| Transport     | tram  | snowmobile         | motorbike     | car    | helicopter | roller     | scooter     |

